 1	# WorldReportsApp - Docker Setup Guide
 2	
 3	## Overview
 4	یہ application World database کے ساتھ مختلف population reports generate کرتی ہے۔ اب یہ Docker کے ساتھ MySQL database کے ساتھ چل سکتی ہے۔
 5	
 6	## Prerequisites
 7	- Docker Desktop installed
 8	- Docker Compose installed
 9	
 10	## Project Structure
 11	```
 12	WorldReportsApp/
 13	├── src/main/java/com/set08103/
 14	│ ├── App.java # Main application
 15	│ ├── DBConnection.java # Database connection
 16	│ ├── Report1_CountriesByPopulation.java # Countries by population
 17	│ ├── Report2_CitiesByPopulation.java # Cities by population
 18	│ ├── Report3_CapitalCitiesByPopulation.java # Capital cities
 19	│ ├── Report4_TopNCitiesByPopulation.java # Top N cities
 20	│ ├── Report5_PopulationDistributionByCountry.java
