| 6 | World population | Yes | ![Report6](screenshots/report6.png) |
| 7 | Population by area (continent/region/country/district/city) | Yes | ![Report7](screenshots/report7.png) |
| 8 | Language speakers (Chinese, English, Spanish) | Yes | ![Report8](screenshots/report8.png) |

## Technology Stack
- **Language**: Java 17
- **Build Tool**: Maven
- **Database**: MySQL 8.0
- **Containerization**: Docker & Docker Compose
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Docker Desktop
- Git

### Running the Application
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/abdulmanan089/SET08103-WorldReports.git
cd SET08103-WorldReports

# Run with Docker
docker-compose up --build
```

## Project Structure
```
SET08103-WorldReports/
├── src/main/java/com/set08103/
│ ├── App.java # Main application
│ ├── DBConnection.java # Database connection
│ ├── Report1_CountriesByPopulation.java # Countries report
│ ├── Report2_CitiesByPopulation.java # Cities report
│ ├── Report3_CapitalCitiesByPopulation.java # Capital cities report
│ ├── Report4_TopNCitiesByPopulation.java # Top N cities report
│ ├── Report5_PopulationDistributionByCountry.java # Population distribution
│ ├── Report7_TotalWorldPopulation.java # World population
│ ├── Report8_PopulationOfArea.java # Area population
│ └── Report9_LanguagePopulation.java # Language statistics
├── world-db/world.sql # World database dump
├── Dockerfile # Application container
├── docker-compose.yml # Multi-container setup
└── pom.xml # Maven configuration
```

## Reports Generated

### 1. Countries by Population
Shows all countries ordered by population (largest to smallest) with:
- Country Code
- Country Name 
- Continent
- Region
- Population
- Capital City

### 2. Cities by Population
Shows all cities ordered by population with:
- City Name
- Country
- District
- Population

### 3. Capital Cities by Population
Shows all capital cities ordered by population with:
- Capital Name
- Country
- Population

### 4. Top N Cities by Population
Shows top N cities where N is user-defined with:
- City Name
- Country
- District
- Population

### 5. Population Distribution by Country
Shows population breakdown for each country:
- Country Name
- Total Population
- Urban Population (with percentage)
- Rural Population (with percentage)

### 6. World Population
Shows total world population: **6,078,749,450**

### 7. Population by Area
Shows population statistics for:
- Continents
- Regions 
- Countries
- Districts
- Cities

### 8. Language Speakers
Shows speaker statistics for major languages:
- Chinese: 1,191,843,539 (19.61% of world)
- Spanish: 355,029,462 (5.84% of world)
- English: 347,077,867 (5.71% of world)

